            <Section1 ID="Sec3">
              <Heading>Results and discussion</Heading>
              <Para>To quantify the enhancement of light absorption, simulation was performed using Computer Simulation Technology (CST) Microwave Studio, Time Domain (TD) Solver [<CitationRef CitationID="CR6">6</CitationRef>]. The simulation model is based on the previously constructed nanowire device without antenna [<CitationRef CitationID="CR2">2</CitationRef>]. The computation of power flow on the surface of the nanowire is obtained by integration of the power density over the nanowire surface.</Para>
