            <Section1 ID="Sec7">
              <Heading>Conclusion</Heading>
              <Para>In this paper, we have shown that the inclusion of bow-tie antenna can increase the ability to absorb light for a wide range of wavelength and can provide the enhancement of sensitivity of the semiconductor photodetector without involving far-field radiation. Thus, the designed nanowire-based nano-antenna system holds promise for both highly sensitive photodetection and photovoltaics applications.</Para>
